{"tid":765980,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"(港豬末日)  ANA計劃擬9至10月取消部份飛往香港班次","createTime":"2018-08-03T08:29:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T06:24:32.000Z","uid":6604,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e5a74e71da26728241e226efdf8b4158015f5da0","tid":765980,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T08:29:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://asahichinese-f.com/travel/news/11724182\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fasahichinese-f.com%2Ftravel%2Fnews%2F11724182&d=ubKrzgiQmVzJPhp33jvs0ttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=8abf6d7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://asahichinese-f.com/travel/news/11724182</a><br />\n<br />\n全日空(ANA)於8月2日宣布，9月1日至10月27日期間將取消3條國際線共212個航班，包含<span style=\"color: red;\">成田機場飛往香港</span>等地的航線在內。屆時將有1萬6500人受到影響。<br />\n<br />\n由於美國波音787型飛機的引擎需進行檢查，ANA方面因而做出此決定；在這之前僅取消過國內線航班，如今也波及國際線。<br />\n<br />\n此外也取消<span style=\"color: red;\">中部機場飛往香港</span>，以及成田機場飛往美國洛杉磯的航班。3航線中平均每天3.7個航班遭取消，在全日空營運的國際線航班當中約佔2%。<br />\n<br />\n該期間的國內線航班取消詳情將於8月9日公布。此外據了解，由於10月28日起為冬季航班，會一併考量引擎檢查工作來編制班表，因此雖然航班減少，但也不會再發生旅客訂票後航班取消的情況。"},{"pid":"517cd4b6c9d9c8d33319a4e1678fc83d0ea98667","tid":765980,"uid":47674,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T08:31:02.000Z","msg":"可唔可以轉用新買嘅A380<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26c987c11abce94285295573b2143729fc999656","tid":765980,"uid":72581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T08:32:02.000Z","msg":"暫時取消兩個月姐"},{"pid":"7e5d497a8d89b0572f94243e23653e37d6dbc834","tid":765980,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"517cd4b6c9d9c8d33319a4e1678fc83d0ea98667","tid":765980,"uid":47674,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T08:31:02.000Z","msg":"可唔可以轉用新買嘅A380<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T08:35:16.000Z","msg":"有都拎嚟救 NRT - LAX 先啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b69eed5f9f1284c8ff29165f4e6fd7e5245c01fe","tid":765980,"uid":140538,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T09:40:46.000Z","msg":"紅葉季<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd27278f2a25f7358eab9bd3e97d8b5f1e4534c8","tid":765980,"uid":3932,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T09:22:12.000Z","msg":"事旦啦 都係搭UO嘅啫"},{"pid":"16b36c7a9e3ab82d4b582cbac1d143088c26eaa5","tid":765980,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bd27278f2a25f7358eab9bd3e97d8b5f1e4534c8","tid":765980,"uid":3932,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T09:22:12.000Z","msg":"事旦啦 都係搭UO嘅啫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T13:43:59.000Z","msg":"試下uo都郁...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06a2616347e17982b9f00a41b19d71f7b041e63f","tid":765980,"uid":45746,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T14:09:32.000Z","msg":"港豬點會搭NH JL呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 全部坐UO奴隸船架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"072dba7587ef19c74d9a290b33203ff843164673","tid":765980,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T14:29:43.000Z","msg":"取消中部去香港係咪笑話<br />\n<br />\n有啲野唔係賺錢問題<br />\n係配合國家發展問題（前提係日本已經係民主國家）"},{"pid":"536cbfce5f65e62f4e6fd0edd062d3e51f791bdd","tid":765980,"uid":96453,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T15:45:09.000Z","msg":"cx都cut冬季航班啦<br />\n根本比Lcc打到pk<br />\n<br />\n仲有港航空姐&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;CX ANA"},{"pid":"5d99453f951462e2596f1c54ae6ed8465d9c5896","tid":765980,"uid":146982,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T15:48:27.000Z","msg":"無影響，港豬只會撘UO <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">答我，幾時有！</span>"},{"pid":"3edcd726f2f4aea3677665391f9dd5c9c0b3d576","tid":765980,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislik